      • getShowFooter

        protected Boolean getShowFooter(MatrixGridBean grid)
        Return true if matrix footer should be displayed. The footer will be displayed if the number of rows exceeds MATRIX_ROW_FOOTER0, which is configurable in sakai.properties as osp.matrixRowFooter. If osp.matrixRowFooter is -1, the footer will never be displayed.
